00:08:32.010 --> 00:08:33.180
If a whole group

00:08:33.180 --> 00:08:34.610
targets one person,

00:08:35.460 --> 00:08:37.220
there must be a reason.

00:08:38.490 --> 00:08:39.490
What era are we in?

00:08:39.700 --> 00:08:40.250
Why are you

00:08:40.250 --> 00:08:41.250
