00:13:55.610 --> 00:13:57.066
the three of you spoke up for me.

00:13:57.066 --> 00:13:57.733
I remember it.

00:13:58.300 --> 00:13:58.820
Thank you.

00:13:59.980 --> 00:14:00.980
